<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Qo&lsquo;llash bo&lsquo;yicha yo&lsquo;riqnoma</span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Keravit<sup>&reg;</sup></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Savdo belgisi:</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Keravit<sup>&reg;&nbsp; </sup></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Chiqarilish shakli:&nbsp; kapsula №___, kapsulalar ichakda eruvchan, o&lsquo;lchami №00. Kapsulaning tarkibi: Jelatin &ndash; 69,01mg, rang beruvchilarsiz, &ldquo;Halol&rdquo; sertifikatiga ega. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Tarkibi: 1 kapsuladagi faol moddalar: laminariya ekstrakti &ndash; 150 mg; tibbiyot achitqisi &ndash; 100 mg; Vitamin B<sub>10</sub> &ndash; 100 mg; vitamin B<sub>5</sub>&ndash; 60 mg; L- sistein &ndash; 40 mg; biotin &ndash; 100 mkg. Yordamchi moddalar: kraxmal, mkts (mikrokristall sellyuloza). </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Shifobaxsh taʼsiri:</span></strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> Keravit<sup>&reg;</sup>ning tarkibidagi laminariya ekstrakti,&nbsp; tibbiyot achitqisi,&nbsp; vitamin B10, vitamin B5, L-sistein hamda&nbsp; biotin&nbsp; bilan bog&lsquo;liq. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Laminariya ekstrakti</span></em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> - qalqonsimon bezning to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri ishlashi uchun zarur bo&lsquo;lgan yod elementi va tirozin aminokislotalarining asosiy tabiiy manbalaridan biri hisoblanadi. Organizmda yod qalqonsimon bezning normal ishlashi uchun zarur bo&lsquo;lgan tiroksin va triyodotironin gormonlarini sintez qilishda ishtirok etadi. Yod bolalar va o&lsquo;smirlarning normal o&lsquo;sishi va rivojlanishi uchun juda muhim, u suyak va tog&lsquo;ay to&lsquo;qimalarining shakllanishida, oqsil sintezida ishtirok etadi, aqliy qobiliyatlarni rag&lsquo;batlantiradi, ish faoliyatini yaxshilaydi va charchoqni kamaytiradi. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Tibbiyot achitqisi</span></em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> - atrof-muhitning salbiy omillari (og&lsquo;ir mehnat sharoitlari, stress) ta&#39;siriga qarshilikni shakllantirishga yordam beradi, oziq-ovqatning so&lsquo;rilishini yaxshilaydi, ichakning transport funktsiyalarini faollashtiradi, immunostimulyatsiya va detoksifikatsiyalovchi ta&#39;sirga ega va organizmni zaharli moddalardan tozalashga yordam beradi. Ovqat hazm qilish sistemasi va jigar faoliyatini rag&lsquo;batlantiradi, moddalar almashinuvini yaxshilaydi hamda ichak mikroflorasining tiklanishiga yordam beradi. Organizmning erta qarish jarayonining oldini oladi. Tibbiyot achitqisi sochlarni salbiy tashqi omillar ta&#39;siridan himoya qiladi, tarkibida sochlarning o&lsquo;sishi uchun kerakli bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp; moddalar biotin mavjud bo&lsquo;lib, u soch ildizlarini&nbsp; namlaydi, soch tolalarining mo&lsquo;rtlashuvidan himoya qiladi va soch to&lsquo;kilishidan asraydi. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Vitamin B10 - ichak mikroflorasi tomonidan o&lsquo;zlashtiriladigan, oqsil biosintezida qatnashmaydigan aminokislota. Vitamin B10&nbsp; oqsillarning normal metabolizmi, qizil qon tanachalari va folik kislotasining shakllanishi, shuningdek melanin pigmenti biosintezi uchun zarurdir. Organizmda barcha hayotiy jarayonlarda faol ishtirok etuvchi vitamin B9 ning struktur komponenti hisoblanadi.&nbsp;&nbsp; Stress yoki B guruhi vitaminlari yetishmasligi natijasida kelib chiqqan oqargan sochlarning rangini tiklashga yordam beradi. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Vitamin B5 (pantoten kislotasi)</span></em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> - - ichak mikroflorasini tiklashda,&nbsp; gemoglobin, neyrotransmitterlar va yog&lsquo;, uglevod va oqsil biosintezlarida ishtirok yetadi. Diqqatni jamlashga yordam beradi, energiyani oshiradi. Eshitish va ko&lsquo;rish qobiliyatini yaxshilaydi, husnbuzarlarni kamaytiradi.&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">L-sistein </span></em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">- sochlar, tirnoqlar va teri keratinining muhim tarkibiy qismi bo&lsquo;lgan aminokislota. Soch o&lsquo;sishini rag&lsquo;batlantiradi va yorqinligini oshiradi.Tirnoq plastinkasini mustahkamlaydi.Terining tuzilishi va holatini yaxshilaydi. Kollagen hosil bo&lsquo;lishini rag&lsquo;batlantiradi. Kuchli antioksidant. Yallig&lsquo;lanishga qarshi ta&#39;sirga ega. Mushak to&lsquo;qimalarining shakllanishiga yordam beradi.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Biotin</span></em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> - soch va tirnoqlarning asosiy tarkibiy qismi bo&lsquo;lgan kollagenning&nbsp; ishlab chiqarilishini rag&lsquo;batlantiradi, soch tuzilishini yaxshilaydi, soch follikulalari hamda tirnoqlarni mustahkamlashga yordam beradi, soch to&lsquo;kilishiga qarshi kurashadi, sochlarning jilokor va&nbsp; qalin bo&lsquo;lishida muhim ahamiyatga ega,&nbsp; yog&lsquo; bezlarining ishini normallashtirib, seboreyaning oldini oladi. Qonda xolesterin darajasini pasaytiradi. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Keravit<sup>&reg;</sup>ni qo&lsquo;llashga ko&lsquo;rsatmalar: </span></span></span></p>

<ul style="list-style-type:square">
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">soch va tirnoqlar mo&lsquo;rtlashuvida;</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">vitaminlar yetishmasligi oqibatida kelib chiqadigan soch to&lsquo;kilish holatlarida;</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">seboreyada;</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">teri holatini yaxshilash;</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">ichak mikroflorasini tiklash;</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">moddalar almashinuvini tartibga solish;</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">husnbuzarlarga qarshi kurashish maqsadida.</span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Qo&lsquo;llash usuli:</span></strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> kuniga 1 kapsuladan 3 mahal. Qabul qilish davomiyligi 1 oydan 3 oygacha. Shifokor ko&lsquo;rsatmasiga binoan preparatni qabul qilish davomiyligi uzaytirilishi mumkin. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Qarshi ko&lsquo;rsatmalar</span></em></strong><em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">:</span></em><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> Homiladorlik va laktatsiya davrida,&nbsp; 8 yoshgacha bo&lsquo;lgan bolalarga shifokor tavsiyasi bilan buyuriladi.&nbsp;&nbsp; Preparat komponentlariga nisbatan yuqori sezuvchanlikda tavsiya etilmaydi. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Nojo&lsquo;ya ta&#39;sirlari:</span></strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> kamdan-kam hollarda ko&lsquo;ngil aynishi, oshqozon buzilishi, bosh og&lsquo;rig&lsquo;i, metiorizm kuzatilishi mumkin. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Dorixonalardan berilish tartibi</span></strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">: shifokor retseptisiz, dori vositasi emas.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt">Ishlab chiqaruvchi:</span></strong><span dir="ltr" lang="UZ" style="font-size:14.0pt"> MCHJ &ldquo;BIO TIME&rdquo; &ldquo;Dina Pharm XOS&rdquo; uchun eksklyuziv <strong>mahsulot. O&lsquo;zbekistonda ishlab chiqarilgan.</strong></span></span></span></p>

